{"tid":276890,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"人生流流長，真係唔明點解啲人會串人遲畢業","createTime":"2017-06-09T07:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T16:15:52.000Z","uid":7110,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05d86e1da626c721d934ed98a5581926599e2e57","tid":276890,"uid":7110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"邊個笑到最後都未知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5585c2b1d43be8197f6b75be332c202d72dd2cf","tid":276890,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:15:34.000Z","msg":"Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2839df44a04682c84f747bf16a14073e15e1b6b8","tid":276890,"uid":7110,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑人遲畢業之餘，仲講到公開試入u先係人生贏家<br />\n真係人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfac50163c086f21d210c238dce50f2c04b9d26","tid":276890,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投行精英鏗哥"},{"pid":"bdc0f672961d3c50381f5682af1903bc693e8b88","tid":276890,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鏗哥我一直都以你為偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67b0571957c0ed52aa1340e4bb770d91f7f7c10","tid":276890,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個笑到最後都未知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同嗰啲中學雞小學雞喺到計人係咪大過自己，考試邊個高啲分啲差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6c02f0f65faf4248c73f6e6536f83551de435f","tid":276890,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46616a0e71ec15f57f00a430a359eaab7d67a426","tid":276890,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"如果以錢為人生目標，遲畢業會吃虧點<br />\n<br />\n客觀來看，遲畢業可能代表遲些進入職場(除非一路翻學一路番工)即使有番兼職，賺的錢也不夠多。而且兼職的工種與你未來的工作也沒什麼關係，遲畢業就代表你少人一些時間上位或累計工作經驗。某程度上影響了就業的發展。<br />\n<br />\n不過在現今社會，如果你有創意，有計劃又去實行，你可能在畢業前已經拋開人地幾條街，甚至中途闖出名堂而離開校園。(大把名人例子)<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"30d86ce14734ef119544b033513d2e7f828f96f0","tid":276890,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果以錢為人生目標，遲畢業會吃虧點<br />\n<br />\n客觀來看，遲畢業可能代表遲些進入職場(除非一路翻學一路番工)即使有番兼職，賺的錢也不夠多。而且兼職的工種與你未來的工作也沒什麼關係，遲畢業就代表你少人一些時間上位或累計工作經驗。某程度上影響了就業的發展。<br />\n<br />\n不過在現今社會，如果你有創意，有計劃又去實行，你可能在畢業前已經拋開人地幾條街，甚至中途闖出名堂而離開校園。(大把名人例子)<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4134c9bcbf598d90000745938da5be4c22dd4a69","tid":276890,"uid":121922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f963bdc766f26a18e2ba82c382ed2ab76dbde50","tid":276890,"uid":120388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}